OL,6,FSir Keir has pledged to bring down net
OL,7,Fmigration; the number of people coming
OL,8,Fto UK from overseas, minus the number
OL,9,Fof people leaving.
OL,11,FIt hit a record high in 2022 at
OL,12,F745,000, before falling around 10 per
OL,13,Fcent last year.
OL,15,FHowever, net migration is still huge
OL,16,Fby historical standards at 685,000.
