OL,7,Fmuch it wants to bring down that
OL,8,Fnumber and critics warn that could
OL,9,Fmake it difficult for the government
OL,10,Fto adequately plan for public services.
OL,12,FThe idea is to train up more UK
OL,13,Fworkers, instead of being so reliant
OL,14,Fof on foreign labour in sectors with
OL,15,Fskills shortages such construction,
OL,16,Fsocial care and health.
