OL,6,FEvans Sarbeng is originally from Ghana
OL,7,Fand works as a nurse at St Cecelia's
OL,8,FCare Home in Scarborough. One of the
OL,9,Fattractions of working in the UK was
OL,10,Fthat he could bring his wife with him
OL,11,Fon his work visa. The ban on bringing
OL,12,Ffamily was introduced earlier this
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,F'I've come in to add value to the
OL,16,Fcommunity,' says student Evans Sarbeng
OL,18,F"If this rule was in place when I was
OL,19,Fapplying to come to the UK, I wouldn't
OL,20,Fhave come here. I would have gone to
OL,21,Fthe US instead," Mr Sarbeng said.
