OL,6,FLet's move on to illegal migration.
OL,7,FLabour will scrap the controversial
OL,8,FRwanda scheme that would have sent
OL,9,Fasylum seekers to the East African
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FInstead the money saved will be spent
OL,13,Fon a new 'border security command',
OL,14,Fhundreds of new investigators with
OL,15,F'counter-terror type powers' as Sir
OL,16,FKeir wants to 'smash the gangs.'
OL,18,FThey also want a returns deal with the
OL,19,FEU, though that will be hard to
OL,20,Fnegotiate.
