OL,6,FSince 2018, nearly 120,000 people have
OL,7,Fcome to the UK by small boats across
OL,8,Fthe channel, many journeys arrange by
OL,9,Fpeople smugglers.
OL,11,FAsylum backlog
OL,13,FThe UK's asylum system costs #4
OL,14,Fbillion a year, has a backlog of
OL,15,Funprocessed claims and at one point #8
OL,16,Fmillion pounds a day was being spent
OL,17,Fon hotel accommodation.
